milestones.description: Asif Masood has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (6) for PAK, going past Majid Khan
de Silva has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (3) for SL, going past Fernando
Majid Khan has broken the record for most sixes (2) in ODIs for PAK, going past Saleem Altaf's 1
Tony Opatha has broken the record for most catches (3) in ODIs for SL, going past Duleep Mendis's 1
Tony Opatha has broken the record for most catches in an innings (2) in ODIs for SL, going past Warnapura's 1
Zaheer Abbas has broken the record for most catches in an innings (2) in ODIs for PAK, going past Asif Masood's 1
Majid Khan and Sadiq Mohammad's 159-run partnership is PAK's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 113 between Sadiq Mohammad and Majid Khan
Majid Khan and Sadiq Mohammad's 159-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 113 between Majid Khan and Sadiq Mohammad
Mushtaq Mohammad and Zaheer Abbas's 88-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 57 between Mushtaq Mohammad and Majid Khan
Pervez Mir and Javed Miandad's 12-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 4 between Mushtaq Mohammad and Wasim Bari
Mevan Pieris and Tony Opatha's 11-run partnership is SL's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 1 between Mevan Pieris and Ranasinghe
Mevan Pieris and de Silva's 23-run partnership is SL's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 6 between Mevan Pieris and Tony Opatha
de Silva and Kaluperuma's 22-run partnership is SL's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 10 between Tony Opatha and de Silva
